title: Jeezy Interview and More
itunes:title: Jeezy Interview and More
description:
Friday 12/15 - Today on the show we had Jeezy stop by where he spoke about his new album "Pressure", the younger generation and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to an Ohio college student who tried to trade chicken Alfredo for sex. Moreover, we opened up the phone lines to see what our listeners thought about the comedian beef between Kevin Hart and Michael Blackson.
